hello tamarawsss, buying broken phones again !! 🫶

wala ka bang time paayos yung iphone mo? or may nakatambak na mga iphone sa bahay niyo na 'di na magamit? 😔

we are buying your defective iphones! let's turn your broken iphones into quick cash ! 💰

what we're looking for 🔍:
ꤥ iphone x, xr, xs, xs max
ꤥ iphone 11, 11 pro, 11 pro max
ꤥ iphone 12, 12 mini, 12 pro, 12 pro max
ꤥ iphone 13, 13 mini, 13 pro, 13 pro max

📍 meet up: near or in FEU campus
🚫 not accepting icloud-locked units & with motherboard issue
✅ apple id must be signed out
✅ must show signs of life (showing of battery logo when plugged into charger, screen is lighting up even if cracked)

interested? send me a message of 💬:
ꤥ iphone model

ꤥ picture of the unit
ꤥ your asking price
ꤥ description of the issue

'wag na kayo mahiyaa, just send me a pm! we also do iphone repairs! pm for more info 🍓
